snippet.title: Digimon Story Cyber Sleuth: Hacker's Memory - Announcement Trailer | PS4, PSVita
snippet.description:
It's time to re-digitize and dive back into the digital world! As Keisuke Amazawa, experience an all new adventure while you work to clear your name, uncover the truth, and protect your friends and family.  Digimon Story Cyber Sleuth: Hacker's Memory will arrive on PS4 and PSVita early 2018.
